creator: IGNITION M
descriptionHtml:
"Pixel-based Fantasy World! Filled with Weaponry!
[Rogue-like] Action!

Raspberry Mash is a challenging action-shooter starring a young girl on a quest for revenge against the gods.
Annihilate all who stand in your way with an expansive arsenal of abilities and weapons,
including swords, spears, lasers, rocket launchers, and more!"
descriptionShort: [FREE] Feel the EXTREME ACTION from pixel graphics!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Finally released!

title: RASPBERRY MASH

creator: IGNITION M
descriptionHtml:
Pixel-based Fantasy World! Filled with Weaponry!
[Rogue-like] Action!

Story of a girl who swore a Revenge against God.
Annihilate all enemies which stand in your way with various weapons.

Evade enemies attack by using Dodge roll!
Feel catharsis through Action and Shooting.

Story will flow every moment by your choices.
Will you able to reach to Real Ending?

Let's move forward by using various Artifacts, Weapons and Skills.

・Mana issue has fixed.
・Some other Error has fixed.
